snippet.title: UFL™ Journey #3 | Core gameplay. Part 2
snippet.description:
Episode #3: Core gameplay. Part 2

We continue to talk about Core gameplay and offer an inside look at how we work on skill moves & shots. And we also touch on goalkeeper animations 🧤
